	<div style="position: relative; top: 6px; left:5px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; padding-left: 45px;">What are the advantages of the Magelo Profile?</div>	
	<div style="position: relative; top: 6px; left:10px;">
<img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/shared/right_menu/support_icone_off.png?v=21" height="15" style="position: absolute; top:0px; left:0px;" width="33" class="png32" /><img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/picto/eq_faq_icone.png?v=21" height="24" style="position: absolute;top:-17px; left:4px;" width="24" class="png32" />	</div>
	<hr class="line">
	<br>
	
	
	<div>The Magelo Profile will properly display the <b class="strong">unbuffed stats</b> for the character, therefore correctly showing the overall worth of the character.<br/>
<br/>
Everything in it <b class="strong">loads quickly</b> into a single window without a need to refresh or wait for tool tips or subsections.<br/>
<br/>
In addition, it has a feature that <b class="strong">breaks down modifiers</b> to list the contributions from enhancements separately from the existing statistics in the piece of equipment viewed. Displaying the contents of the bags and the money carried is also optional.<br/>
<br/>
Those without a guild can add a <b class="strong">Looking for Guild</b> feature in their profile that shows recruiting guilds information about their availability.<br/>
<br/>
The profile window is <b class="strong">entirely customizable</b> by the user and features the character <b class="strong">without advertisements</b> or unrelated items in the background.<br/>
<br/>
You can <b class="strong">sync your character whenever you want and as much as you want</b>. You are in control!<br/>
<br/>
<br/>
<br/>
<img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/eq/faq/general_2.jpg?v=-1" align="absmiddle" border="0" /></div>
	<br>
	
